title: 1940 South Sydney Rabbitohs season
text: The 1940 South Sydney Rabbitohs season was the 33rd in the <a href="South%20Sydney%20Rabbitohs">club's</a> history. The club competed in the <a href="New%20South%20Wales%20Rugby%20League%20premiership">New South Wales Rugby Football League Premiership (NSWRFL)</a>, finishing the season 6th.
